Nigerian actor, Blossom Chukwujekwu has received a beautiful birthday message from his ex-wife, Maureen after turning a day older on Monday, November 4, 2019. Recall that the couple made headlines back in September after the news broke that their once admired marriage had crashed.Sharing his photo, she simply wrote: “Happiest Birthday Bubba” The couple had been known for their sweet displays of affection on social media and it came as a huge surprise that their union crashed after three years together. Source